prompts.frontCover:
Minimalist greeting card front, 2D flat illustration. A charming and humorous beach scene with a clean, simple aesthetic against a soft cream background. In the center, cartoon illustrated versions of Lao Lao (person on the left in the photo) and Jordan (person on the right in the photo) are building a giant sandcastle together. The sandcastle is comedically shaped like a massive Chinese food takeout box, complete with tiny sand chopstick details sticking out of the top. Jordan is patting the "box" with a small shovel, and Lao Lao is adding a "scallion" made of seaweed to the top, both with happy, laughing expressions. They are wearing the same jackets from the reference photo, but adapted for a beach setting (unzipped or worn casually). Tiny, simple waves lap at the edge of the scene.

Centered above the illustration, the text reads "Happy Anniversary, Lao Lao!" in a beautiful, readable, and elegant handwritten cursive script. The overall composition is balanced, lighthearted, and stylish.
